When a gamer and homebody starts the BUFF for traveling through time and space, he certainly chooses to make waves! Make waves! And make waves! Domineering cat lady, Lori fox lady, Girly rabbit lady…This is not a Zoo! This is a fantastic Another World under the rule of the law of the jungle! In a real strategic game and a huge conspiracy crisis, the Overlord of Another World is emerging, with the rest nothing but losers…
(Source: Webnovel)

Kang Jin-Hyeok, a perpetual D-rank hunter. Unable to level up due to large guilds controlling hunting grounds, he scraped by with part-time jobs. One day, a dungeon appears in his room. "Is this... a dungeon?" Having exclusive access to the dungeon, Jin-Hyeok begins to grow stronger as he successfully hunts and levels up... "Just you wait, you big guild bastards who looked down on me! I will become stronger, with this dungeon!" (Source: Naver Webtoon, translated)
